542
00:33:18.270 --> 00:33:21.870
IPH5201 is a CD39

543
00:33:21.930 --> 00:33:22.650
inhibitor.

544
00:33:23.770 --> 00:33:27.330
As illustrated in this figure, CD39 is an

545
00:33:27.350 --> 00:33:31.130
