551
00:33:47.990 --> 00:33:51.310
adenosine by downstream CD73.

552
00:33:52.910 --> 00:33:53.510
Conversely,

553
00:33:54.530 --> 00:33:58.490
blocking CD39 enhance dendritic cells

554
00:33:58.630 --> 00:34:01.710
activation through ATP accumulations

555
00:34:02.450 --> 00:34:05.690
and also restores T cell stimulation by

556
00:34:05.750 --> 00:34:07.850
