557
00:34:09.591 --> 00:34:13.571
As illustrated in the figure on the right, IPH5201

558
00:34:13.870 --> 00:34:17.630
is a humanized Fc silent IgG1

559
00:34:17.830 --> 00:34:21.571
inhibiting both membrane and soluble

560
00:34:21.611 --> 00:34:22.551
