757
00:46:13.582 --> 00:46:17.162
In the past few years, the treatment landscape for select patients with

758
00:46:17.462 --> 00:46:20.842
resectable non-small cell lung cancer has evolved

759
00:46:20.852 --> 00:46:21.542
